name: p41n.net (inside the modem)
description: I found about selling #NFT and #Cryptoart a couple months ago. Everything started off great! I was really excited to join a community of liked minded people and grow in a art space unlike anything I ever experienced before. Until last night. I was sucked into my computer screen..Can't really comprehend if I have left my physical body and I can't really describe what exactly I am seeing now since it's nothing I have ever seen before. Some how I am able to continue to have access to all my account through this database that looks like its from lawnmowerman. I will report more and more as I go on. I can't really figure out how to use the system from in side the network but i am slowly configuring it to show you what happened to me in the last 24hrs
